          "description": "Baron Herzog, Budapest; Axel Ryden, Stockholm, 1918; Osborn Kling, Stockholm, 1934 (sale: H. Bukowski, Stockholm, September 25-26, 1934, no. 323, illus. pl. 37); Thorsten Laurin, Stockholm, 1938, and his daughter Mrs. B. Stjernsward, Sakanor, Sweden (sale: Sotheby's, London, June 24, 1970, no. 4, illus.); [Old Masters Gallery, London]; [H. Shickman Gallery, New York]. Mr. and Mrs. William H. Marlatt Fund, 1971.",
