      "tombstone": "Portrait of Count Jean-Antoine Chaptal, 1824. Antoine-Jean Gros (French, 1771-1835). Oil on canvas; framed: 183.5 x 151.1 x 16.5 cm (72 1/4 x 59 1/2 x 6 1/2 in.); unframed: 136.5 x 114.3 cm (53 3/4 x 45 in.). The Cleveland Museum of Art, Leonard C. Hanna, Jr. Fund 1964.54",
      "current_location": "201 French Neoclassical Painting & Sculpture",
      "title": "Portrait of Count Jean-Antoine Chaptal",
      "title_in_original_language": null,
