      "tombstone": "Villerville Seen from Le Ratier, 1855. Charles François Daubigny (French, 1817-1878). Oil on fabric; framed: 80 x 141.5 x 7.5 cm (31 1/2 x 55 11/16 x 2 15/16 in.); unframed: 54.2 x 116.2 cm (21 5/16 x 45 3/4 in.). The Cleveland Museum of Art, Bequest of William G. Mather 1951.323",
      "current_location": "220 19th Century European",
