      "tombstone": "Young Woman with a Turban, c. 1780. Jacques-Louis David (French, 1748-1825). Oil on canvas; framed: 76 x 66 x 8 cm (29 15/16 x 26 x 3 1/8 in.); unframed: 55.2 x 46 cm (21 3/4 x 18 1/8 in.). The Cleveland Museum of Art, Gift of George S. Kendrick 1952.542",
      "current_location": "216B French and German",
      "title": "Young Woman with a Turban",
      "title_in_original_language": null,
